---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" currentPage="/about">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12 mb-16 inset">
      <img src="/profile.png" alt="Profile"
        class="w-36 h-36 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-full shadow-2xl border-4 border-accent-400 object-cover flex-shrink-0 animate-scale-in" />
      <div
        class="bg-brand-900/90 dark:bg-brand-800/90 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-2xl border border-brand-800 backdrop-blur-sm flex-1 w-full">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-300 to-accent-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          About Me</h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Full-stack developer passionate about
          creating meaningful digital experiences that solve real-world problems and delight users.</p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">With expertise in modern web technologies and
          a keen eye for design, I transform complex ideas into elegant, scalable solutions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="space-y-16">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-200 mb-4">Background</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed text-lg">As a dedicated developer, I've built a diverse
          portfolio ranging from comprehensive web applications to interactive gaming experiences. My journey
          includes creating a full-stack music discovery platform with Spotify API integration, developing tourism
          websites with responsive design, and crafting engaging web-based games. I believe in learning through
          building real projects that solve actual problems.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-200 mb-4">What I Do</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent-300">Frontend Development</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">Creating responsive, accessible user interfaces with modern frameworks like
              React and Vue.js, combined with CSS frameworks like Tailwind CSS for pixel-perfect designs.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent-300">Backend Development</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">Building robust server-side applications with Node.js and PHP, designing
              efficient databases with MySQL, and creating secure RESTful APIs for seamless integration.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent-300">API Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">Connecting external services and APIs, including third-party platforms like
              Spotify, payment gateways, and cloud services to enhance application functionality.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent-300">Performance Optimization</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">Analyzing and improving application performance through code optimization,
              caching strategies, and efficient database queries for fast, responsive user experiences.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-200 mb-4">Key Achievements</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-500 pl-6 py-2">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent-300 mb-2">Music Recommendation Platform</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">Developed a full-stack web application with Spotify API integration, user
              authentication, and social features serving music enthusiasts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-500 pl-6 py-2">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent-300 mb-2">Tourism Portal</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">Created a comprehensive tourism website for Malaysian destinations,
              demonstrating full development lifecycle from planning to deployment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-500 pl-6 py-2">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent-300 mb-2">Interactive Games</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300">Built engaging web-based games using JavaScript and Phaser3, showcasing
              creative problem-solving and interactive design skills.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-200 mb-6">Technologies & Tools</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="chip">Java</span>
          <span class="chip">PHP</span>
          <span class="chip">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="chip">Python</span>
          <span class="chip">C#</span>
          <span class="chip">HTML5</span>
          <span class="chip">CSS3</span>
          <span class="chip">Tailwind CSS</span>
          <span class="chip">React</span>
          <span class="chip">Node.js</span>
          <span class="chip">MySQL</span>
          <span class="chip">MongoDB</span>
          <span class="chip">Git</span>
          <span class="chip">GitHub</span>
          <span class="chip">Docker</span>
          <span class="chip">REST APIs</span>
          <span class="chip">Spotify API</span>
          <span class="chip">Phaser3</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-200 mb-4">Beyond Code</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">When I'm not coding, you'll find me exploring new
          technologies, contributing to open-source projects, or sharing knowledge with the developer community. I
          believe in continuous learning and staying up-to-date with the latest web development trends and best
          practices. I'm also interested in UI/UX design principles and enjoy creating intuitive user experiences.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent-200 mb-4">Let's Work Together</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6 text-lg">I'm always excited to collaborate on new projects and ideas.
          Whether you have a specific project in mind or just want to discuss possibilities, feel free to reach
          out.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          Get In Touch
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
